[[File:Diplomatic missions of the Cook Islands.svg|thumb|450px|Map of diplomatic missions of the Cook Islands {{legend|#ff0000|Cook Islands}}{{legend|#212178|Cook Islands embassy}}{{legend|#aaccff|Cook Islands embassy, non-resident}}]]
This page lists the '''Diplomatic missions of the [[Cook Islands]]'''. Although the Cook Islands is an [[associated state]] of [[New Zealand]], {{Numrel|CK|alt2=it maintains |diplomatic relations with|states|O=Y}}. The Cook Islands has one diplomatic mission abroad (a high commission in New Zealand). This high commission has multiple accreditation.{{#tag:ref|High commission in New Zealand is accredited also to [[Australia]], [[Fiji]] and [[Papua New Guinea]].<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.ck/whoswho.htm |title=The Cook Islands Who's Who |website=Cook Islands website |date= |accessdate=2016-01-29 |quote=Jonassen, Dr Jon Tikivanotau Michael, MBE...Cook Islands High Commissioner to New Zealand, Australia, Fiji and Papua New Guinea 1997-1999}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.foreignaffairs.gov.fj/foreign-missions/foreign-missions-accredited-to-fiji-from-wellington |title=Foreign Missions accredited to Fiji from Wellington |publisher=Ministry of Foreign Affairs of Fiji |year=2012 |accessdate=2016-01-29 |quote=Cook Islands High Commission...Wellington}}</ref>|group="note"}} The Cook Islands also has a number of [[honorary consul]]ates.{{#tag:ref|There are honorary consuls based in [[Australia]] ([[Sydney]]), [[Monaco]] ([[Monaco]]),<ref>{{cite web|title=Principality of Monaco |url=http://www.mfai.gov.ck/index.php/contact-us/overseas-offices/64-principality-of-monaco.html |publisher=Cook Islands Ministry of Foreign Affairs & Immigration |date= |accessdate=2016-01-23 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160130103229/http://www.mfai.gov.ck/index.php/contact-us/overseas-offices/64-principality-of-monaco.html |archivedate=2016-01-30 |df= }}</ref> [[Norway]] ([[Oslo]]) and [[Turkey]] ([[Istanbul]]). There were also honorary consuls based in the [[United States]] ([[Honolulu]] and [[Los Angeles]]).<ref>{{cite book |title=Cook Islands Investment, Trade Laws and Regulations Handbook |isbn=1433075660 |publisher=Lulu.com| page=30 |year=2015 }}</ref>|group="note"}}
